sub_title: Don't call it a dream. Call it a plan. - Career Coach & Trainer in personal/professional development and communication.
summary:
Unfold your true potential - CareerWise! 

As a cross cultural career & vision coach I help people and organizations grow, turn plans into actions and thus reach their career goals faster and more efficiently. 

My key services are (for individuals and companies): 

-Conduct career workshops and personal one-to-one coachings
-Provide valuable trainings to improve both verbal and non-verbal communication skills, such as presentation techniques & body language in job interviews
-Help develop & maintain a can-do attitude and positive mindset 
-Support and review of resumé & cover letter creation in English & German
-Create a life/business vision in line with their true ambitions.

I am open to collaborations and opportunities with companies that want to improve the future of their employees, students or people. 

Looking forward to hearing from you!
